reviewText:
DO NOT BUY THIS GAME IF YOU HAVE WINDOWS 7 64BIT !!!

Ok, here's the long review;
i get a 'can't initiliaze' error message upon starting the game, and apparently I'm not the only.

I've read through the community posts and none of their tricks were working for me;

The one thing I didn't try was turning off the UAC, and no, I'm not going to cripple security of my system for one game;

The fault of this whole mess lies with Steam for selling it in the first place, i don't expect old games to be compatible forever, but i do expect people who sell them to make sure they'll work on the majority of the OS's out there
